#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:129
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Select Account Type</guilabel> screen will be next if the "
#| "wizard cannot determine your account type. Select your account type from "
#| "the list (if you do not know, you will need to contact your email "
